From Edward Gornish Subject Radar Laser Detectors What are people's opinions about laser detectors Escort makes a laser detector the Passport and claims it works However I've talked to some people who have said that it will only work if you are lucky if the cop happens to point his laser at a car in front of you and the laser beam happens to reflect back to your Otherwise it won't Regular radar of course travels in all directions hence it is more Any comments Escort has a deal till the end of April I think where if you buy their wideband Passport X K Ka and laser detectors you'll save off of buying them In this case the addition of the laser detector over the Passport is only Passport normally costs Eddie Gornish University of Illinois Center for Supercomputing Research Development